flowchart LR
    Source[(源数据库)]

    subgraph platform [迁移平台]
        direction TB
        Ctrl[集中管控]

        subgraph base [基础服务]
            CM[集群管理]
            RM[资源管理]
            HA[高可用]
            Meta[元数据管理]
        end

        subgraph structFull [结构与全量]
            Collect[结构采集与转化]
            SchemaMig[结构迁移]
            FullFlow[全量数据流]
        end

        subgraph incrRead [日志读取]
            Reader[Reader]
            Filter1[Filter]
            Queue[Queue]
        end

        subgraph incrWrite [同步写入]
            Filter2[Filter]
            Mapping[Mapping]
            Conflict[冲突检测]
        end

        AI[AI智能<br/>映射建议与异常诊断]

        Ctrl --> base
        base --> structFull
        structFull --> incrRead
        incrRead <--> incrWrite
        AI -.-> Collect
        AI -.-> Conflict
    end

    Target[(目标数据库)]
    MQ[消息队列]

    Source --> platform
    platform --> Target
    platform --> MQ
